\paragraph{Overview} 
We design task-specific prompts for the LLM that explore two IE variants for graph construction.
In the first variant, termed Neon({{2411.12449_FO0022||FO}}), LLM generates news entity-interactions {{2411.12449_FO0023||FO}} using only the subject {{2411.12449_FO0024||FO}} and the corresponding news chunk {{2411.12449_FO0025||FO}} that mentions {{2411.12449_FO0026||FO}}. In the second variant, {{2411.12449_FO0027||FO}} is generated by incorporating both the subject {{2411.12449_FO0028||FO}} and object {{2411.12449_FO0029||FO}} entities, along with the news chunk {{2411.12449_FO0030||FO}} that contains mentions of both ({{2411.12449_FO0031||FO}}, {{2411.12449_FO0032||FO}}).